                <h3 class="card-title">Springfield Armory National Historic Site</h3>
                <br/>
                <p>For nearly two centuries, the U.S. Armed Forces and American industry looked to Springfield Armory for innovative engineering and superior firearms. Springfield Armory National Historic Site commemorates the critical role of the nationâ€™s first armory by preserving and interpreting the world's largest historic US military small arms collection, along with historic archives, buildings and landscape.</p>
